ygData.msgSnippet: I heard a price of about 500pp quoted on Innoruuk three weeks ago (the last time I had access to a computer with a 3D card), which seems a tad high for an item
ygData.messageBody:
I heard a price of about 500pp quoted on Innoruuk three weeks ago (the last time I had access to a computer
with a 3D card), which seems a tad high for an item with no documented features. hehe

Kenross Cantoforjado, 24 songs, Innoruuk
